#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
yoga-tray  v2.0
Combined system tray app for the Lenovo Yoga 9i Gen 7.

Each menu section is a TraySection subclass that implements:
  read_state()          → current state from hardware/disk
  update_display(state) → update all widgets for that state
  build_menu_items()    → list of Gtk widgets for this section

The base class provides for free:
  - Periodic polling (set poll_interval_ms)
  - Change detection (no spurious redraws or notifications)
  - Debounced desktop notifications
  - Immediate UI update on user action (apply_change)
  - State refresh on every menu open

Requires: python3-gi
Optional: gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1, gir1.2-notify-0.7
"""

